com.nwawsoft.util.datastructures

Class Graph.GraphNode

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.nwawsoft.util.datastructures.Graph.GraphNode
  • Enclosing class:
    Graph

    public static class Graph.GraphNode
extends java.lang.Object
    Defines GraphNode objects as they are used in the Graph class. A GraphNode has a name, a list of edges to other GraphNode objects including their respective edge weights (often referred to as edgeWeights or edgeWeight) and are either marked or not marked (controlled by the boolean marked).
